CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 5, 1941, pg. 12 reads: "National Officers, Delegates And Visitors To Debs About Town Confab In Pittsburgh"...bottom, left to right; Muriel Sutherland, New York; Hazelle Lomax, Boston; Thelma E. Butler, Boston; Fedelma Boyd, Cleveland...- Harris Photos"
TitMainTitle: Debs About Town members, from left: Muriel Sutherland, Hazelle Lomax, Thelma E. Butler, and Fedelma Boyd posed on Loendi Club porch
